Package campfunctions

package campfunctions
  • Class
    Description
    CampController
    An abstract class representing a controller for camp-related operations.
    CreateCamp
    A class representing the functionality to create a new camp.
    DeleteCamp
    A class representing the functionality to delete a camp.
    EditCamp
    A class representing the functionality to edit a camp.
    IEnrolls
    This interface is implemented by WithdrawCamp and RegisterCamp.
    RegisterCamp
    The RegisterCamp class represents a functionality to register for camps It implements the IEnrolls interface and includes methods to enter camp informations.
    SearchCamp
    Class for searching camps in a CampList.
    StaffCreatedCamp
    The StaffCreatedCamp class represents a functionality to view camps created by staff It implements the IViewData interface and includes methods to retrieve and display information about the camps.
    StudentRegistered
    StudentRegistered class implements IViewData for viewing information about students registered in camps.
    ToggleVisibility
    ToggleVisibility class extends CampController for managing the visibility of a camp.
    ViewCampCommittee
    ViewCampStudent class implements the IViewData interface for handling camp data.
    ViewCampStaff
    ViewCampStudent class implements the IViewData interface for handling camp data.
    ViewCampStudent
    ViewCampStudent class implements the IViewData interface for handling camp data.
    ViewRegisteredCampStudent
    This class implements the functionality for viewing data of registered camp students.
    WithdrawCamp
    WithdrawCamp class implements the IEnrolls interface for handling camp withdrawals.
